A vintage-style illustrated aerial view of Singapore's downtown skyline at dusk, featuring distinctive skyscrapers and the harbor in warm amber and teal tones. In the foreground, a cozy rooftop terrace on a high floor shows silhouettes of people gathered casually around small tables, their figures backlit by the golden sunset reflecting off glass towers. Paper lanterns glow softly overhead, creating an intimate community atmosphere against the sprawling urban backdrop. The composition evokes 1960s travel poster aesthetics with slightly muted colors, gentle grain texture, and bold geometric shapes in the architecture.
